</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="40.[151,1436,151,588]" box="[196,763,301,327]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[196,403,301,327]" pageId="40" pageNumber="41">Elevation range:</emphasis>
